cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use ComfyUI-Spellcaster in your work, please cite it as below."
title: "ComfyUI-Spellcaster: Architecture-aware nodes for AI image generation"
abstract: >
  A set of ComfyUI custom nodes that auto-detect model architecture
  (SD 1.5, SDXL, Illustrious, ZIT, Flux Dev, Flux 2 Klein, Chroma, Flux Kontext),
  load the correct CLIP and VAE, enhance prompts via local LLM,
  and sample with architecture-optimal settings.
authors:
  - name: "Le Laboratoire Sonore"
repository-code: "https://github.com/laboratoiresonore/ComfyUI-Spellcaster"
license: "LicenseRef-NOPE"
type: software
keywords:
  - comfyui
  - stable-diffusion
  - flux
  - diffusion-models
  - text-to-image
